{"tid":2227123,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"致：有想過歸還銅紫荊星章的你","createTime":"2020-10-02T13:52:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-02T14:03:54.000Z","uid":240362,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"9afaa7a506b08a46dec4e48765a017528fc98faf","tid":2227123,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-02T13:52:14.000Z","msg":"如果在2020年前獲頒到銅紫荊星章，你可以和朋友說：「奧運會拎到獎牌嗰個單車選手李慧詩都係拎呢個星章」，但在2020打後這個星章將會迎來一個超重大變化，每一位即將及曾經被獲頒這個星章的人，都將會非常棹忌一句說話：「係唔係姐係『荷蘭叻』都拎過嗰個？」<br />\n<br />\n如果說諾貝爾文學獎因為頒予邱吉爾 (Winston Churchill)，反由得主帶給獎項更高一層的榮譽；那麼吧銅紫荊「荷蘭水蓋」頒予陳百祥，我將會理解成：「自此以後，就只有荷蘭叻會為到曾經得到呢個水蓋而感到光榮。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/personal/%E8%87%B4-%E6%9C%89%E6%83%B3%E9%81%8E%E6%AD%B8%E9%82%84%E9%8A%85%E7%B4%AB%E8%8D%8A%E6%98%9F%E7%AB%A0%E7%9A%84%E4%BD%A0/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpersonal%2F%25E8%2587%25B4-%25E6%259C%2589%25E6%2583%25B3%25E9%2581%258E%25E6%25AD%25B8%25E9%2582%2584%25E9%258A%2585%25E7%25B4%25AB%25E8%258D%258A%25E6%2598%259F%25E7%25AB%25A0%25E7%259A%2584%25E4%25BD%25A0%2F&d=ooVnpwewILBg1HoWGmAtmZtjV1Wc7Scp8ABb8MCffMw%3D&h=5876137d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpersonal%2F%25E8%2587%25B4-%25E6%259C%2589%25E6%2583%25B3%25E9%2581%258E%25E6%25AD%25B8%25E9%2582%2584%25E9%258A%2585%25E7%25B4%25AB%25E8%258D%258A%25E6%2598%259F%25E7%25AB%25A0%25E7%259A%2584%25E4%25BD%25A0%2F&h=af0cad87\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/personal/%E8%87%B4-%E6%9C%89%E6%83%B3%E9%81%8E%E6%AD%B8%E9%82%84%E9%8A%85%E7%B4%AB%E8%8D%8A%E6%98%9F%E7%AB%A0%E7%9A%84%E4%BD%A0/</a>"},{"pid":"e8cbb2766ecd9ec6146268c11124bf6ad323cb60","tid":2227123,"uid":98117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-02T13:56:04.000Z","msg":"如果你已經唔記得當初喺為咩而行出嚟，當初喺為咩而憤怒，就入嚟睇下條片<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n【自由之歌】有個香港人無收錢整咗條咁嘅片出嚟<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2224648\" da